  <brief_title>Esomeprazole And Symptomatic Response In Patients With Or Without An Elevated Risk For Non-Steroidal Anti-Inflammatory Drug (NSAID)-Associated GI Damage</brief_title>
  <acronym>Synchronise</acronym>
  <official_title>SYNCHRONISE: Esomeprazole 20 mg Once Daily for Relief of Upper Gastrointestinal Symptoms Associated With Continuous Use of NSAIDs Including COX-2 Selective NSAIDs in Dutch General Practice: The Influence of Risk-Factors for NSAID-Associated GI Damage on Sympton Response</official_title>
  <sponsors>
